	<div class="grid md:grid-cols-[1fr_200px] gap-12 items-start">
		<article class="prose prose-slate prose-lg text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
			<h1 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-900 mb-8">About Me</h1>
			<p>
				Hello! I'm Susamn. I've been building software for over 10 years, navigating the chaotic but exciting world of distributed systems and cloud infrastructure.
			</p>
			<p>
				Currently, I work as a Senior Software Engineer, where I focus on developer tooling. My philosophy is simple: <strong>build tools that get out of the way</strong>. I believe the best infrastructure is the kind you don't have to think about.
			</p>
			<h3>What I do</h3>
			<ul>
				<li><strong>Engineering:</strong> I specialize in Go, Rust, and TypeScript. I love diving deep into performance optimization and system architecture.</li>
				<li><strong>Open Source:</strong> I'm an active contributor. You'll often find me fixing bugs or improving documentation for the tools I use daily.</li>
				<li><strong>Writing:</strong> I use this site to document my learnings. Writing helps me clarify my thoughts and (hopefully) help others solving similar problems.</li>
			</ul>
